<body>
Reports a pointless or pointlessly complicated boolean expression or statement.
<p>Example:
<pre><code>
  let a = !(false && x);
  let b = false || x;
</code></pre>
<p>After the quick fix is applied the result looks like:
<pre><code>
  let a = true;
  let b = x;
</code></pre>
</body>
